snippet.title: Joe Scott
snippet.description:
Ask Questions. Get interesting, amazing, funny, inspiring, eye-opening, mind-shifting, informative answers. Every week.

This is the home of Answers With Joe, where I take questions and comments and deconstruct them to find the interestingness - the funny, unique, but universal truths that give you a new perspective on the world. Enter with an open mind. Leave with a blown one. New videos every Monday unless I screw up.

Follow me @answerswithjoe on:
Facebook
Twitter
Snapchat
Instagram

Want to mail me something? I totally take bribes:

Answers With Joe
PO Box 180391
Dallas, TX 75218
